HEADWORD: Fuscin
<hw>Fus"cin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>fuscus</ets>
dark-colored, tawny.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol. Chem.)</fld> <def>A brown,
